{"abstract": "http://act.yapc.eu/ye2016/talk/6790", "blasters": ["perl"], "description": "<h2>From 12:00 jump to 18:00 when the presentation continues</h2>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://telegram.org/\">Telegram</a> is an app for secure instant messaging, which provides a great API for building bots.\nI will go through its main API functionality and will demonstrate some examples of real bots that I use in my practice.\n\n<ul>\n   <li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Telegram_(software)\">Telegram on wikipedia</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pavel_Durov\">Pavel Durov</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://metacpan.org/pod/WWW::Telegram::BotAPI\">WWW::Telegram::BotAPI</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://metacpan.org/pod/Telegram::Bot\">Telegram::Bot</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://metacpan.org/pod/Telegram::BotKit\">Telegram::BotKit</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://metacpan.org/pod/Bot::ChatBots::Telegram\">Bot::ChatBots::Telegram</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>A home monitoring devide using Arduino. Taking pictures and sending messages if the picture has changed.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n", "event": {"name": "YAPC - European Perl Conference 2016", "nickname": "yapc-eu-2016", "twitter": "yapceu", "url": "http://act.yapc.eu/ye2016/"}, "featured": "2016-11-26", "file_date": "2016-12-03", "filename": "andrew-shitov-bots-for-telegram-yapceurope-2016", "length": "33:22", "recorded": "2016-08-24", "short_description": "From 12:00 jump to 18:00 when the presentation continues Telegram is an app for secure instant messaging, which provides a great", "speaker_twitters": " @andrewshitov", "speakers": {"andrew-shitov": {"episodes": [], "hosting": [], "info": {"city": "Amsterdam", "country": "The Netherlands", "github": "ash", "home": "http://shitov.ru/", "name": "Andrew Shitov - \u0410\u043d\u0434\u0440\u0435\u0439 \u0428\u0438\u0442\u043e\u0432", "twitter": "andrewshitov"}, "videos": [{"event": {"name": "YAPC - European Perl Conference 2016", "nickname": "yapc-